description:
Knuckles, the Malevolent Nun is a wonderfully funny series about a grotesquely ugly nun with an attitude to match her looks. Knuckles, however unorthodox, is a likable character. She is constantly accompanied by Witchbite, a talking crow sent by God to observe her. She is also constantly being courted by Lucifer, the prince of darkness, who also happens to wear nothing except a pair of briefs and a pumpkin on his head. Sadly for the course of true love, he is continually denied Knuckles affection.

Like anyone else, Knuckles has her dark side. For one thing, she excels at passing off bird excrement as art, making her millions of dollars. This doesnt exactly bode well for her vows.

The series premiered in 1991 and was created by Cornelius Stone and Roger Langridge.
name: Knuckles The Malevolent Nun

description: When tentacled bug-eyed monsters from the moon use their advanced technology to travel through time and change history its up to the Metaphysical Police to put things right. The Metacops, consisting of Albert Einstein, Leonardo DaVinci, Nikola Tesla and led byJayne Mansfield are charged with making sure history is not manipulated. And it doesnt matter if the aliens do have a contract with President Lyndon Johnson and need this job to help their bottom line. Roman centurions who become werewolves, female foreign legionnaires on moas and talking elephants seem almost normal compared to Einstein and DaVinci firing a particle beam canon from a zeppelin.
name: Metacops

description:
Timelines is comic book series by Fun Publications where they publish their Transformers fiction. The stories are released in conjunction with BotCon and the Transformers Collectors' Club. Stories are contain both original timelines as well as build on existing continuities.

Note: in 2014 Fun Publications included the original Transformers Timelines #1 - Descent into Evil into their numbering resulting in that years issue being #10 instead of #9. Issue #9 was released later as a digital exclusive comic.
name: Transformers Timelines
